@startuml onboarding_flow
!include https://raw.githubusercontent.com/plantuml-stdlib/C4-PlantUML/master/C4_Container.puml

title GoFuture - Процесс онбординга нового партнера (Tenant Provisioning Flow)

' Use sequence diagram for process flow
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam sequenceParticipantBorderColor #2C3E50
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBorderColor #7F8C8D
skinparam sequenceGroupBorderColor #2E86C1
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FCF3CF

actor "Партнер (partner_owner)" as Partner
participant "Partner Portal" as Portal #85C1E9
participant "Tenant Provisioning Service" as TPS #8E44AD
participant "Keycloak (IdP)" as Keycloak #E74C3C
database "Tenant Registry" as Registry #1A5276
database "PostgreSQL" as DB #1A5276
participant "Pricing Service" as Pricing #2E86C1
participant "Notification Service" as Notif #2E86C1
participant "Grafana" as Grafana #27AE60
participant "API Gateway (Kong)" as Kong #E67E22

== Шаг 1: Регистрация (5 мин) ==

Partner -> Portal : Заполнить форму регистрации (название, контакты, tier, регион)
Portal -> TPS : CreateTenantRequest {name, tier, region, admin_email}
TPS -> Registry : INSERT tenant (status: PROVISIONING)
TPS --> Portal : tenant_id + status: PROVISIONING

== Шаг 2: KYC/KYB верификация (1-2 дня) ==

note right of TPS
  Полуавтоматическая проверка:
  - API проверки (ЕГРЮЛ / Companies House)
  - Ручной review Compliance team
  - Результат: APPROVED / REJECTED
end note

TPS -> Registry : UPDATE status: KYC_PENDING
TPS -> TPS : KYC API checks (автоматические)
TPS -> TPS : Compliance review (ручной)
TPS -> Registry : UPDATE status: KYC_APPROVED

== Шаг 3: Договор и tier (1 день) ==

TPS --> Partner : Email: KYC одобрен, подпишите договор
Partner -> Portal : Подписать договор (DocuSign API)
Portal -> TPS : ContractSigned {tier: Business, plan: standard_sea}
TPS -> Registry : UPDATE tier, contract_id

== Шаг 4: Automated Provisioning (< 10 мин) ==

group Saga: Tenant Provisioning [Автоматическая, идемпотентная]

    TPS -> Keycloak : 4.1 Create realm: tenant-{name} + Create roles: partner_owner, partner_admin, ... + Create admin user + Configure SSO broker (если указан IdP)
    Keycloak --> TPS : realm_id, admin_user_id

    TPS -> DB : 4.2 Provision database: [Business tier] CREATE RLS policy for tenant_id = {uuid} [Enterprise tier] CREATE SCHEMA tenant_{name}
    DB --> TPS : schema/RLS ready

    TPS -> Pricing : 4.3 Create pricing plan: default tariffs for region + surge settings + commission rate
    Pricing --> TPS : pricing_plan_id

    TPS -> Notif : 4.4 Create notification templates with branding: logo, colors, name
    Notif --> TPS : templates_created

    TPS -> Kong : 4.5 Create rate limit policy per tenant: {tier_limits} + API key generation
    Kong --> TPS : api_key, rate_limit_id

    TPS -> Grafana : 4.6 Provision monitoring: - Tenant dashboard (auto) - Alert rules (SLA thresholds) - Billing meter config
    Grafana --> TPS : dashboard_url

end

TPS -> Registry : UPDATE status: PROVISIONED

== Шаг 5: Sandbox (30 мин - 2 дня) ==

TPS -> TPS : 5.1 Create sandbox: seed data (test drivers, zones)
TPS --> Partner : Email: sandbox ready + API docs URL + sandbox API key + dashboard URL

Partner -> Portal : 5.2 Configure SSO (upload IdP metadata or OIDC discovery URL)
Portal -> Keycloak : Configure SSO broker + test connection
Keycloak --> Portal : SSO verified

Partner -> Portal : 5.3 Customize: branding, pricing, notification templates
Portal -> TPS : UpdateTenantConfig

note right of Partner
  Партнер тестирует:
  - API-интеграцию (sandbox)
  - SSO login flow
  - Создание тестовых поездок
  - Проверку уведомлений
end note

TPS -> Registry : UPDATE status: SANDBOX

== Шаг 6: Go-Live (5 мин) ==

Partner -> Portal : Запросить активацию production
TPS -> TPS : Pre-flight checks: - SSO configured? + - API tested? + - Contract signed? + - KYC approved? +
TPS -> Kong : Switch API key: sandbox -> production
TPS -> Registry : UPDATE status: ACTIVE
TPS --> Partner : Email: Production активирован! 🎉 + Production API key + Support channel

note right of TPS
  SLA мониторинг активирован.
  Billing metering начат.
  Tenant dashboard: live data.
end note

@enduml
